This project needs gcc 4.4 minimum to compile. It has been tested with
gcc 4.4.2, 4.4.3 and gcc 4.5. Lately it compiles slowly with any
version of gcc below 4.5

If you have checked nyah out from git, please fetch the chilon library
dependency using:
    git submodule update --init

This project is organised like this:
    doc/website/    - The nyah website
    src/
        chilon/     - Library used by this project. git submodule
        nyah/
            grammar/  - Nyah grammars
                grammar.nyah  - Nyah grammar meta-grammar source.
                nyah.nyah     - Nyah meta-grammar source.
            std/      - Nyah standard library
            mousebear/        - Bootstrap nyah compiler.
                builder/          - mousebear AST -> code
                    cpp.hpp, cpp.cpp   -  C++0x code generator
                grammar/          - mousebear chilon::parser grammar
                    grammar.hpp   - grammar-grammar
                    nyah.hpp      - nyah grammar
